            <title>[PIG-2176] add logical plan assumption checker </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2176</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Pig expects certain things about LogicalPlan, and optimizer logic depends on those to be true. Could that verifies that these assumptions are true will help in catching issues early on. &lt;br/&gt;
Some of the assumptions that should be checked - &lt;br/&gt;
1. All schema have valid uid . (not -1).&lt;br/&gt;
2. All fields in schema have distinct uid. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
